Package: libggui-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: ggui-dev
Description: Cross-platform terminal UI library for C++ (development files)
 GGUI is a lightweight, cross-platform terminal user interface toolkit
 written in modern C++17. This development package provides the headers,
 static library, and pkg-config metadata required to build applications
 that use GGUI.